message.body: Today is painfully slow.
I'm sorry: ( listen to music? Does that help?
Not if I don't have anything to do.
I'm thinking about taking an early lunch
You mean just one of us going away?
Are things still slow? Did you eat lunch?
Haha that's sad. But for us it'd be great. We'd wind up on the ceiling without even knowing or trying.
I took a break
I don't know what to do when I get back
Haha. We've had more passionate hugs after an eight hour work day than they have had after several weeks of seeing each other. And I have seen this on person. It's true. Baby. We just got it.
Why is there nothing to do? You can't do sky roc?
Hahaha that's hilarious
Not really cause I wouldn't want to be caught
Is this just because you're to good and ahead of the game, waiting for others to get their stuff done?
Yeah
Of course
Haha. Of course.
Oh my god. The piece of steak you gave me is pretty much raw! After microwaving.
My other pieces werent
Mine either.
It's ok. I'm just saying.

Hah. When Megan had her baby shower so many people were there. Gifts, money, food and desserts. Tian is supposedly having a bridal shower right now. Only a few people are there basically eating lunch brought in by someone.
Haha good
I want that right now
D:
We're just having a salad with eggs and lunch meat and stuff. A chef salad I think. Just giving you a heads up in case you wanted soothing more substantial. God knows I do. Haha.
Haha okay
Do you remember we went to a target with Cassy? And it had a Starbucks
Um. I don't know. Was this in ocean city Maryland or on the way? I know we went to done chain store then.
It was on.city line avenue in Philly
Oh
I was definitely not there
Okay that's what Cassy said too. I thought we were all there and ran into her little cousins. She has me thinking I was dreaming
Ok let me know if you do get food. I'm looking at this salad and I am way too hungry.
Want me to get you something?
I have no idea what I would get. I would only very something if you do. I'll just find something else here if you don't.
I'm not. But I'd get you something. I'm skying at 7:30
No it's ok. Are you skyping here?
Yeah
Ok. See you soon.
I have leftover chips and salsa from chipotle. I don't know if thats good enough
Mm. I'm thinking about ordering a burger. I'm so hungry. But you can bring them.
If I do, the burger won't meet the minimum. Did you want something?
I'm not gonna be hungry but if you really need to order me a burger and I'll eat it tomorrow
Haha. Ok. I'll see.
You have literally done/said nothing but supposedly laugh at a joke or something funny. Pointless! !
Thanks again for taking care of me last night.
Your mom said I should put tea bags on it tonight.
You are very welcome. I will always take care of you. And yes. The tea bags may help. I will do that for you.
Thanks :)
Come straight home tonight and shower so that I can do the yes bags dinner rather than later. And also because we didn't get much time together last night.
Okay
Good
